<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-54-0297 </DOCNO><TEXT>The article reviews the ICRP publications and recommendations for monitoringintakes of radioactive materials. The latest ICRP publication in thisfield, Publication 54, forms a technical document for radiation protectionpersonnel concerned with applying the recommendations published by theICRP in other connections to the individual monitoring of internal contamination.</TEXT></DOC>